<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you have </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">found a cheaper quote elsewhere and wish to submit this for our Price Promise</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> - we will beat any like for like quote* - please </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">send us a screenshot/attachment detailing the competitor name, levels of cover and price</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. We will then submit this to our underwriters for approval.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>*For full details and terms and conditions, please click here.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
